

'''Léon Mugesera''' (wavutse 1952)  ni umugabo wo mu Ruanda kandi yahoze atuye i Québec , muri Kanada . Yirukanywe muri Kanada kubera ijambo rirwanya kurwanya abatutsi abamunenga bavuga ko ari intangiriro ya jenoside yo mu Rwanda mu 1994.<ref>https://www.lapresse.ca/international/afrique/2020-11-27/affaire-leon-mugesera/le-rwanda-condamne-pour-traitement-cruel-et-inhumain.php</ref>
